name: Nike Air Force 1 Low
description: The definition of a classic. This all-white icon features crisp leather edges and the durability that made it a street staple in Nairobi and beyond.
curatorNote: Clean, versatile, and essential. Keep them fresh.

name: Adidas Samba OG
description: Born on the pitch, adopted by the streets. The Samba features a soft leather upper and suede overlays to recreate the look and feel of the original.
curatorNote: The gum sole adds that vintage touch that works with everything from shorts to cargos.

name: Air Jordan 4 'Military Black'
description: A modern flip on the 1989 classic. Featuring premium white leather, neutral grey suede, and black accents for a sharp, versatile look.
curatorNote: Arguably the cleanest Jordan 4 colorway of the decade. A serious flex.
